My attempts to bring up a crafting sandbox keep failing with nginx not being able to spin up. (https://instabase.sandboxes.site/sandboxes/weimingwu)
This is a branch that is a direct fork of master and nothing else, so it shouldn't have any issues
I'm seeing this in the nginx logs:
```+ '[' 1 = 1 ']'
+ docker rm -f nginx
+ exec /var/workspace/daemons/bin/nginx.sh
Error from server (NotFound): configmaps "nginx-conf-tmpl" not found```

Hey there, could you try following the remediation covered in this? https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1729535824964379?thread_ts=1729529491.208329&channel=C05L87V014J&message_ts=1729535824.964379 (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1729535824964379?thread_ts=1729529491.208329&channel=C05L87V014J&message_ts=1729535824.964379)
